official_title: A bill to amend the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act to designate the lower Wisconsin River for potential addition to the national wild and scenic rivers system.

summary.text: Designates the lower Wisconsin River (from the dam at Prarie du Sac, Wisconsin, to its confluence with the Mississippi River at Prarie du Chien, Wisconsin) for potential addition to the wild and scenic rivers system under the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act. (Adds 16 U.S.C. 1276(a)(27))

titles.title: A bill to amend the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act to designate the lower Wisconsin River for potential addition to the national wild and scenic rivers system.
